data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!!!!  PRICE REDUCED!!!!!  PRICE REDUCED!!!!!  PRICE REDUCED!!!!!  55+ COMMUNITY! LOVELY AND LARGE!!  THIS HOME SITS ON A VERY LARGE LOT AND THE HOME IS 1824 SQUARE FEET.  OWN THE LAND IN MURRIETA HOT SPRINGS COMMUNITY THAT SITS NEXT TO THE "SOON TO BE OPEN" MURRIETA HOT SPRINGS LUXURY RESORT/SPA.  A CORNER LOT THAT HAS LOW MAINTENANCE FRONT AND BACKYARDS.  LONG DRIVEWAY FOR TANDEM PARKING IN FRONT, CONCRETE PORCH AND DOUBLE DOOR ENTRY.  LIVING ROOM IS GOOD SIZE AND HAS A NICE WINDOW FOR NATURAL LIGHT.  SEPARATE FORMAL DINING ROOM BETWEEN LIVING ROOM AND KITCHEN WITH BUILT IN HUTCH IN DINING ROOM.  KITCHEN HAS DISHWASHER, STOVE AND OVEN.  WINDOW TO THE FRONT ABOVE SINK.  FAMILY ROOM/DINETTE (YOU DECIDE) OPEN TO KITCHEN WITH BAR.  LAUNDRY ROOM HAS EXTRA CABINET SPACE AND DESK AREA. GUEST BATHROOM WITH SHOWER OVER TUB AND A DOOR TO THE GUEST BEDROOM.  SECOND BEDROOM IS VERY NICE SIZE WITH MIRRORED WARDROBE DOORS. GOOD SIZE PRIMARY BEDROOM WITH ATTACHED PRIMARY BATHROOM. SPA TUB AND SEPARATE SHOWER.  THIS HOUSE IS CHARMING AND VERY CLEAN. LOCATED IN THE SPRING KNOLLS ASSOCIATION, CLOSE TO CLUBHOUSE WITH LOTS OF ACTIVITIES AND SUMMER BBQS AND FRIENDLY PEOPLE, SHOPPPING, MALL AND FREEWAYS.  JUST WAITING FOR YOU!! THANKS FOR SHOWING.  ** SEE AGENT REMARKS FOR IMPORTANT INFORMATION.**
